text: Cancellicula aethiopica is a species of sea snail, a marine gastropod mollusk in the family Cancellariidae, the nutmeg snails. ==Description== The shell grows to a length of 4 mm. ==Distribution== This species occurs in the Indian Ocean off Somalia. ==References== * Verhecken A.
